{"tid":1030554,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"左手有一個如針孔的小血洞傷口","createTime":"2019-02-21T04:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T13:37:19.000Z","uid":3204,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"95be8f3c243f513144d9a7d05154cf3a2cb6b266","tid":1030554,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:46:31.000Z","msg":"天水圍疑現「拮針狂徒」！昨晚（19日）一名女子與友人行經置富銀座，被一名迎面而來的男子碰撞，感到手臂被「拮」，隨即驚叫，對方雖有道歉但急步離開，女事主隨即查看撞及處，發現長袖衣物下，左手有一個如針孔的小血洞傷口，女事主擔心不已，趕往天水圍醫院求診，並報警處理。警方將案件暫列襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，暫時無人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d95cd902196e3838618f27888249d9598e802f","tid":1030554,"uid":32439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:53:38.000Z","msg":"J黎姐，嚇我唔到嘅"},{"pid":"f1f29f1fc136c7b027f68da68de3c4658d30df98","tid":1030554,"uid":90499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:53:58.000Z","msg":"愛滋針<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d1d1c0c33614e1816009f4852c4a21d94fb199","tid":1030554,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1f29f1fc136c7b027f68da68de3c4658d30df98","tid":1030554,"uid":90499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:53:58.000Z","msg":"愛滋針<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:56:59.000Z","msg":"第一時間都係諗起呢樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6b54a8fb85f6e05d93813b3f757deae0393a24","tid":1030554,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:57:31.000Z","msg":"又開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df052ae34ffdd0c9af4c105e0ad516ff9b030ad1","tid":1030554,"uid":67225,"like":0,"disl